pxSQLStatementPost: SELECT "PC0"."pxurgencyassign" AS "pxUrgencyAssign" , "PC0"."pxrefobjectinsname" AS "pxRefObjectInsName" , "PC0"."pylabel" AS "pyLabel" , "PC0"."pyassignmentstatus" AS "pyAssignmentStatus" , "PC0"."pyinstructions" AS "pyInstructions" , "PC0"."pyassignmentstatus" AS "pyAssignmentStatus" , "PC0"."pxdeadlinetime" AS "pxDeadlineTime" , "PC0"."pxassignedoperatorid" AS "pxAssignedOperatorID" , "PC0"."pxupdateoperator" AS "pxUpdateOperator" , "PC0"."pxupdatedatetime" AS "pxUpdateDateTime" , "PC0"."pxgoaltime" AS "pxGoalTime" , "PC0"."pxcreatedatetime" AS "pxCreateDateTime" , "PC0"."pxtasklabel" AS "pxTaskLabel" , "PC0"."pxassignedusername" AS "pxAssignedUserName" , "PC0"."pxrefobjectclass" AS "pxRefObjectClass" , "PC0"."pxrefobjectkey" AS "pxRefObjectKey" , "PC0"."pxapplication" AS "pxApplication" , "PC0"."pzinskey" AS "pzInsKey" FROM pegadata.pc_assign_worklist "PC0" WHERE  ( "PC0"."pxassignedoperatorid" = ?  AND "PC0"."pxworkgroup" = ?  )  AND "PC0"."pxobjclass" = ?  ORDER BY 1 DESC, 7 ASC
